
# Install Coursier
```
$ brew install coursier/formulas/coursier
```

# Install Metals

https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.scalameta/metals_2.12

```
$ coursier bootstrap \
  --java-opt -Xss4m \
  --java-opt -Xms100m \
  --java-opt -Dmetals.client=emacs \
  org.scalameta:metals_2.12:0.11.1 \
  -r bintray:scalacenter/releases \
  -r sonatype:release \
  -o /usr/local/bin/metals-emacs -f
```

# Install Ispell
```
$ brew install ispell
```

